
=Typology=

Julien Lecaille distinguishes:

* LSC Legal Service for Commons : provides domain names, etc.. exists already in Lille, northern France

* FSC Financial Service for Commons : manages financial accounts and flows for non-legal entities

* DSC Digital Service for Commons : manages digital infrastructures on behalf of the commoners

